SELECT [q].[Question], [q].[Distributor], [q].[PartyHllcode], [q].[PartyMasterCode], CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NOT NULL AND [t].[Answer] IS NOT NULL THEN [t].[Answer]
    ELSE N''
END, CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NOT NULL AND [t].[PhotoData] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[PhotoData]
FROM [QuestionsNew] AS [q]
LEFT JOIN [Tbl_ReviewAnswers] AS [t] ON [q].[Distributor] = [t].[Rscode]
WHERE CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) >= @__startDate_0 AND CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) <= @__endDate_1 AND [t].[Rscode] = @__rscode_2 AND [t].[EmpNo] = @__UserId_3 AND [t].[QuestionId] = [q].[QuestionId] AND [t].[Outlet] = [q].[PartyHllcode]
ORDER BY [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
